<p><a title="Approved Provider List Brochure" class="sys_21" href="/docs/About-us/Approved-Provider-List-Brochure.pdf">Support brokerage:</a>&nbsp;Support brokers work with you to help you find the support that is right for you.</p>
<h2>Feedback and Complaints</h2>
<p>If you disagree with your allocated budget or what you are allowed to spend the money on then please click on the <a target="_blank" class="sys_16" href="https://www.nhs.uk/NHSEngland/complaints-and-feedback/Pages/nhs-complaints.aspx">NHS Complaints Procedure</a> for guidance.</p>
